import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.sort_values(by='date')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.plot(data['date'], data['wounds'], label='wounds')
    ax.plot(data['date'], data['other'], label='other')
    ax.plot(data['date'], data['disease'], label='disease')
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the trend of wounds, other and disease over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['wounds'].plot(kind='hist', bins=20, color='blue', edgecolor='black', alpha=0.5)
    plt.axvline(data['wounds'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['wounds'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['wounds'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['wounds'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wounds?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    plt.hist(data['disease'], bins=10, color='green', alpha=0.5)
    plt.axvline(data['disease'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['disease'].mean():0.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['disease'].median(), color='blue', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['disease'].median():0.2f}")
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of disease?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')
    ax.scatter(data['wounds'], data['other'], data['disease'], c='r', marker='o')
    ax.set_xlabel('Wounds')
    ax.set_ylabel('Other')
    ax.set_zlabel('Disease')
    plt.title('What is the correlation between wounds, other and disease?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
